data.description: Ranch home on .38 acres. Partial fenced yard. Mature trees and landscaping. There is a gas log fireplace in the living room It has not been used. There is no propane tank connected to it. The Primary bedroom has a door to the covered back deck. There is an open deck off the kitchen on the side of the house. A new roof and gutter guards were installed in 2022. LVP flooring in the living room, hallway and one bedroom.
